#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:255
msgid "Base domain"
msgstr "Domaine de base"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:256
msgid ""
"Root domain for artist subdomains, e.g. agnosis.art. Each artist is "
"reachable at nicename.{base_domain}. Requires a wildcard DNS record (*."
"{base_domain}) pointing to this server. Leave blank to disable subdomain "
"routing."
msgstr ""
"Domaine racine pour les sous-domaines des artistes, par exemple agnosis.art. "
"Chaque artiste est accessible à l'adresse nicename.{base_domain}. Nécessite "
"un enregistrement DNS générique (*.{base_domain}) pointant vers ce serveur. "
"Laissez vide pour désactiver le routage par sous-domaine."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:261
msgid "Node label"
msgstr "Étiquette du nœud"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:262
msgid "How this node introduces itself to the network."
msgstr "Comment ce nœud se présente-t-il au réseau."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:269
msgid "Email driver"
msgstr "Pilote de messagerie"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:277
msgid "Artwork submissions address"
msgstr "Adresse de soumission des œuvres"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:278
msgid "Artists send artwork to this address — e.g. submit@agnosis.art"
msgstr ""
"Les artistes envoient leurs œuvres à cette adresse — par exemple "
"submit@agnosis.art"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:282
msgid "Biography submissions address"
msgstr "Adresse de soumission des biographies"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:283
msgid "Artists send biography updates to this address — e.g. bio@agnosis.art"
msgstr ""
"Les artistes envoient leurs mises à jour de biographie à cette adresse — par "
"exemple bio@agnosis.art"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:287
msgid "Event submissions address"
msgstr "Adresse de soumission d'événements"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:288
msgid ""
"Artists send event announcements to this address — e.g. event@agnosis.art"
msgstr ""
"Les artistes envoient leurs annonces d'événements à cette adresse — par "
"exemple event@agnosis.art"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:292
msgid "Replace artwork address"
msgstr "Remplacer l'adresse de l'œuvre"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:293
msgid ""
"Artist sends a new version of an existing artwork. Subject must match the "
"original title. Bypasses duplicate detection — e.g. replace@agnosis.art"
msgstr ""
"L'artiste envoie une nouvelle version d'une œuvre existante. Le sujet doit "
"correspondre au titre original. Contourne la détection de doublons — par "
"exemple replace@agnosis.art"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:297
msgid "Removal request address"
msgstr "Adresse de demande de suppression"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:298
msgid ""
"Artist requests takedown of an existing artwork. Subject must match the "
"title. Moves the post to draft pending admin review — e.g. remove@agnosis.art"
msgstr ""
"L'artiste demande la suppression d'une œuvre existante. Le sujet doit "
"correspondre au titre. Déplace le message en brouillon en attente de "
"validation par l'administrateur — par exemple remove@agnosis.art"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:302
#, fuzzy
msgid "Promote artwork address"
msgstr "Remplacer l'adresse de l'œuvre"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:303
msgid ""
"Artist sends an email here (subject = exact artwork title) to mark that "
"artwork as featured in their gallery overview. Any previously featured "
"artwork is automatically demoted — e.g. promote@agnosis.art"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:307
msgid "Photo-only address"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:308
msgid ""
"Opt-out lane for photographers and lens-based artists whose photograph is "
"the artwork, not a snapshot of it. Submissions here are published with the "
"original image exactly as sent — AI enhancement is skipped and the quality-"
"rejection gate is bypassed. AI description (title, tags, alt text) still "
"runs. Use the [Photo] subject indicator as a fallback for mail clients that "
"do not support To: aliases — e.g. photo@agnosis.art"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:312
msgid "Goodbye / self-removal address"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:313
msgid ""
"Artist emails here (any subject, no attachment needed) to request account "
"deletion. A confirmation link is emailed back before anything is deleted — e."
"g. goodbye@agnosis.art"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:319
msgid "IMAP host"
msgstr "Hôte IMAP"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:320
msgid "e.g. imap.yourhost.com"
msgstr "par exemple imap.votrehôte.com"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:324
msgid "IMAP port"
msgstr "Port IMAP"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:331
msgid "Use SSL"
msgstr "Utiliser SSL"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:339
msgid "Skip SSL certificate validation"
msgstr "Ignorer la validation du certificat SSL"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:344
msgid ""
"⚠ Use only as a temporary workaround when your mail server's certificate is "
"not yet trusted (e.g. Plesk self-signed cert before Let's Encrypt is applied "
"to the mail daemon). Disable this once the mail server presents a valid "
"certificate."
msgstr ""
"⚠ Utiliser uniquement comme solution temporaire lorsque le certificat de "
"votre serveur de messagerie n'est pas encore reconnu (par exemple, "
"certificat auto-signé Plesk avant que Let's Encrypt ne soit appliqué au "
"démon de messagerie). Désactivez ceci une fois que le serveur de messagerie "
"présente un certificat valide."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:348
msgid "IMAP username"
msgstr "Nom d'utilisateur IMAP"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:349
msgid ""
"Login username for the IMAP account — typically the catch-all mailbox "
"address."
msgstr ""
"Nom d'utilisateur de connexion pour le compte IMAP — généralement l'adresse "
"de la boîte aux lettres catch-all."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:353
msgid "Submission email password"
msgstr "Mot de passe de l'e-mail de soumission"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:359
msgid "Webhook secret"
msgstr "Secret du webhook"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:360
msgid "HMAC secret shared with your webhook provider (Mailgun, SendGrid…)."
msgstr ""
"Secret HMAC partagé avec votre fournisseur de webhook (Mailgun, SendGrid…)."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:366
msgid "Inbox retention (days)"
msgstr "Rétention de la boîte de réception (jours)"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:372
msgid ""
"Seen IMAP messages and processed/failed queue rows older than this are "
"permanently deleted by the daily cleanup. Default: 7 days."
msgstr ""
"Les messages IMAP lus et les lignes de file traitées/échouées plus anciennes "
"que cette durée sont définitivement supprimés par le nettoyage quotidien. "
"Par défaut : 7 jours."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:378
msgid "Per-sender hourly submission limit"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:385
msgid ""
"Maximum submissions accepted from a single artist per hour, across both IMAP "
"and webhook intake. Exceeding this limit silently drops the message (no "
"retry from ESPs). Default: 5."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:390
msgid "Require SPF/DKIM authentication"
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:393
msgid ""
"When enabled, intake messages must pass SPF or DKIM authentication (via the "
"Authentication-Results header). Prevents spoofed From: addresses. Requires "
"your ESP to include Authentication-Results headers and your domain to have "
"SPF/DKIM records configured. Leave off if you are not sure — rejected "
"legitimate mail is silent. Default: off."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:399
msgid "Description provider"
msgstr "Fournisseur de description"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:407
msgid ""
"Analyses the artwork image and writes the title, body, tags and alt text. "
"WordPress AI Services delegates to whichever provider the site has "
"configured via the AI Services plugin."
msgstr ""
"Analyse l'image de l'œuvre et écrit le titre, le corps, les tags et le texte "
"alternatif. Les services AI de WordPress délèguent à celui que le site a "
"configuré via le plugin AI Services."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:411
msgid "OpenAI vision model"
msgstr "Modèle de vision OpenAI"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:413
msgid ""
"Model used for artwork description when OpenAI is the description provider. "
"Must support vision input."
msgstr ""
"Modèle utilisé pour la description de l'œuvre lorsque OpenAI est le "
"fournisseur de description. Doit supporter l'entrée de vision."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:417
msgid "Anthropic model"
msgstr "Modèle Anthropic"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:419
msgid ""
"Model used for artwork description when Anthropic is the description "
"provider. Must support vision input."
msgstr ""
"Modèle utilisé pour la description de l'œuvre lorsque Anthropic est le "
"fournisseur de description. Doit supporter l'entrée de vision."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:425
msgid "Enhancement provider"
msgstr "Fournisseur d'amélioration"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:428
msgid "Auto (OpenAI if key is set)"
msgstr "Auto (OpenAI si la clé est configurée)"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:430
msgid "Disabled — use original image"
msgstr "Désactivé — utiliser l'image originale"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:433
msgid ""
"Enhances the artwork image before publishing. Uses OpenAI gpt-image-1. Set "
"to Disabled to skip enhancement and publish the original."
msgstr ""
"Améliore l'image de l'œuvre avant publication. Utilise OpenAI gpt-image-1. "
"Mettre sur Désactivé pour sauter l'amélioration et publier l'originale."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:437
msgid "OpenAI image model"
msgstr "Modèle d'image OpenAI"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:439
msgid ""
"Model used for image enhancement when OpenAI is the enhancement provider."
msgstr ""
"Modèle utilisé pour l'amélioration d'image lorsque OpenAI est le fournisseur "
"d'amélioration."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:445
msgid "Polish biography with AI"
msgstr "Polir la biographie avec l'IA"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:448
msgid ""
"When enabled, biography submissions are passed through the AI to fix "
"spelling and make minor text improvements before saving."
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'il est activé, les soumissions de biographie sont traitées par l'IA "
"pour corriger l'orthographe et apporter de légères améliorations au texte "
"avant de sauvegarder."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:452
msgid "Polish events with AI"
msgstr "Polir les événements avec l'IA"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:455
msgid ""
"When enabled, event submissions are passed through the AI to fix spelling "
"and make minor text improvements before saving."
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'il est activé, les soumissions d'événements sont traitées par l'IA "
"pour corriger l'orthographe et apporter de légères améliorations au texte "
"avant de sauvegarder."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:461
#, fuzzy
msgid "Merge biography updates with AI"
msgstr "Polir la biographie avec l'IA"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:464
msgid ""
"When enabled, biography updates are merged with the existing biography using "
"AI — new information is integrated rather than replacing everything. "
"Recommended: artists can send incremental updates (\"I just won an award\") "
"without resubmitting their full bio. Disable to always replace the biography "
"with the latest submission."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:470
#, fuzzy
msgid "Rejection threshold (quality score)"
msgstr "Seuil d'amélioration (score de qualité)"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:478
msgid ""
"Photos scoring at or below this value (1–10) are automatically rejected — "
"the artist receives a friendly email explaining the issue and is invited to "
"resubmit. Score 0 disables automatic rejection. Must be lower than the "
"enhancement threshold. Default: 3."
msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:483
msgid "Enhancement threshold (quality score)"
msgstr "Seuil d'amélioration (score de qualité)"

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:491
msgid ""
"Photos scoring below this value (1–10) are automatically enhanced. Score 10 "
"= perfect photograph, 1 = technically unusable. Default: 7 — only visibly "
"problematic photos are processed. Set to 1 to disable automatic enhancement "
"entirely."
msgstr ""
"Les photos avec une note inférieure à cette valeur (1–10) sont "
"automatiquement améliorées. Score 10 = photo parfaite, 1 = techniquement "
"inutilisable. Par défaut : 7 — seules les photos visiblement problématiques "
"sont traitées. Mettre à 1 pour désactiver complètement l'amélioration "
"automatique."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:497
msgid "OpenAI API key"
msgstr "Clé API OpenAI"

